content:
@tante Bitcoin = original transferable, digital entity w/ 100% use case. It patented the Blockchain.

All Crypto coins (or Tokens) are by definition, derivatives  of Bitcoin ... either directly (via forks) such as Litecoin and DASH ... or indirectly such as ETH, Polkadot, Cardano, etc.
renderedContent:
